lenic Socialist Movement|PASOK]]<br>{{Percentage bar|8.44|c=green}}\n|[[Golden Dawn (Greece)|XA]]<br>{{Percentage bar|8.23|c=black}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Results 2012 June|url=http://ekloges-prev.singularlogic.eu/v2012b/public/#|publisher=Ministry of Interior|accessdate=26 January 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''[[Greek legislative election, January 2015|January 2015]]'''\n|[[Coalition of the Radical Left|SYRIZA]]<br>{{Percentage bar|34.42|c=pink}}\n|[[New Democracy (Greece)|New Democracy]]<br>{{Percentage bar|29.58|c=blue}}\n|[[Golden Dawn (Greece)|XA]]<br>{{Percentage bar|7.44|c=black}}\n|[[The River (Greece)|The River]]<br>{{Percentage bar|6.36|c=cyan}}\n|[[Independent Greeks|ANEL]]<br>{{Percentage bar|5.32|hex=38A3E7}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Results 2015|url=http://ekloges.ypes.gr/current/v/public/index.html#|publisher=Ministry of Interior|accessdate=26 January 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''[[Greek legislative election, September 2015|September 2015]]'''\n|[[Coalition of the Radical Left|SYRIZA]]<br>{{Percentage bar|33.62|c=pink}}\n|[[New Democracy (Greece)|New Democracy]]<br>{{Percentage bar|29.46|c=blue}}\n|[[Golden Dawn (Greece)|XA]]<br>{{Percentage bar|7.83|c=black}}\n|[[Communist Party of Greece|KKE]]<br>{{Percentage bar|5.14|c=red}}\n|[[Panhellenic Socialist Movement|PASOK]]<br>{{Percentage bar|4.44|c=green}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Election 2015 September|url=http://ekloges.ypes.gr/current/v/public/index.html|publisher=Ministry of Interior|accessdate=26 September 2015}}</ref>\n|}\n|}\n\n==Members of Parliament==\n\n===Current members===\n*[[Theodoros Dritsas]] ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Costas Douzinas]]  ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Georgia Gennia]]  ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Eleni Stamataki]]  ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Konstantinos Katsafados]] ''[[New Democracy (Greece)|ND]]''\n*[[Nikos Kouzilos]] ''[[Golden Dawn (Greece)|XA]]''\n\n=== Members of Parliament (Jan 2015 - Sep 2015)===\n*[[Theodoros Dritsas]] ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Stathis Leoutsakos]] ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n*[[Eleni Stamataki]] ''[[SYRIZA]]''\n